107
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:03,279
Exactly. Scum like Ye Yunzhou

108
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:04,199
isn't worth your hands.

109
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,839
You dare talk?

110
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:09,639
You disappeared three years
without a word,

111
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,240
only to bring back this trash.

112
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,519
And now you stop me?

113
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:13,279
You...

114
